jobs.description: At Kicks Flagship Store, I am responsible for the Kiehl's counter, a brand I am passionate about and proudly stand behind. My work mainly consists of assisting customers with expert knowledge in skincare, as well as taking care of the counter by cleaning, meeting budget goals, and driving sales forward.

I started with a summer temporary position in the beauty department, which transitioned into a part-time role. My work primarily involved assisting customers and providing suitable advice based on their needs. During my time at Åhléns, I was also given the opportunity to work for the brand Dior, and I became manager for the Dior counter in the department store.

During my time as a waitress, high demands were placed on being service-oriented, stress-resistant, and able to deliver a great experience for the guests. I was also in charge of the time schedule and responsible for training new employees.
